{{Infobox website | name = Just10 | logo = Just10 icon.png | logo_size = 150px | company_type = Corporation | foundation = {{Start date|2014}} | location = [[Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada]] | area_served = | founder = [[Frederick Ghahramani]] | chairman = | chairperson = | president = | MD = | CEO = [[Frederick Ghahramani]] | GM = | key_people = | industry = [[social network]] | products = | services = | revenue = | operating_income = | net_income = | assets = | equity = | owner = | num_employees = | parent = | divisions = | subsid = | programming_language = [[C++]], [[Objective-C]], [[Javascript]], [[Node.js]], Pliant, [[Java (programming language)|Java]] | ipv6 = | alexa = | website_type = | advertising = | registration = Open | num_users = | language = Multilingual | launch_date = | current_status = Live Public Beta | collapsible = | collapsetext = | caption = | footnotes = | intl = | website = {{URL|1=https://just10.com/|2=just10.com}} }}
'''Just10 Incorporated''' ('''Just10'''), is an advertising-free private social network where users are limited to having just 10 friends, and all content, posts, and messages are strictly private, and are permanently deleted in 10 days.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Cuthbertson |first1=Anthony |title=Just10: Privacy Advocate Launches Social Network for 'Real Friends' | url=http://www.newsweek.com/just10-privacy-advocate-launches-social-network-real-friends-421651|accessdate=1 February 2016|publisher=Newsweek|date=February 1, 2016}}</ref> The company was started by privacy advocate and technology entrepreneur [[Frederick Ghahramani]].
